name: Free Wave Hazy IPA
description: Free Wave is a hugely hoppy hazy IPA with a juicy body and velvety pour. A trio of Amarillo, Citra and Mosaic hops generate bodacious aromatics of tangerine and grapefruit. Notes of pine and florals emerge in the secondary palate for an herbaceous reprieve in all the right places. It’s luscious, smooth, and highly aromatic.

name: Nova Zero
description: Inspired by Nova Scotia’s iconic wine, Nova 7 by Benjamin Bridge Vineyards, Nova Zero is a groundbreaking non-alcoholic experience delivering the unmistakable characteristics that have made its namesake a symbol of the East Coast. Enjoy this fresh and elegant thirst quencher anytime, anywhere.
